OL,3,CPoliticians in Wales vote to approve
OL,4,Cassisted dying services on Welsh NHS
OL,6,FPoliticians in Wales have voted to say
OL,7,Fthe Senedd should have powers to
OL,8,Fintroduce assisted dying services on
OL,9,Fthe NHS, if a landmark law passes in
OL,10,FWestminster.
OL,12,FThe Senedd played host to a debate and
OL,13,Fvote on the technicalities of where
OL,14,Fdecision-making should lie when it
OL,15,Fcomes to introducing such a service,
OL,16,Fnot on the principle of assisted dying
OL,17,Fitself.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
