OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772016033
OL,3,CPoliticians in Wales vote to approve
OL,4,Cassisted dying services on Welsh NHS
OL,6,FMembers of the Senedd voted to approve
OL,7,Fthe principle of such services being
OL,8,Favailable on the NHS on Tuesday, 24
OL,9,FFebruary.
OL,11,FA majority of the current Senedd
OL,12,Fpreviously expressed opposition to the
OL,13,Fprinciple of assisted dying, most
OL,14,Frecently before today in a vote in
OL,15,FOctober 2024.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
