PN,46306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772016033
OL,3,CPoliticians in Wales vote to approve
OL,4,Cassisted dying services on Welsh NHS
OL,6,FSome of those who argued for Senedd
OL,7,Fmembers to vote 'no' are supporters of
OL,8,Fthe principle of assisted dying, but
OL,9,Fcritics of the legislation.
OL,11,FSimilarly, some of those who argued
OL,12,Ffor a 'yes' vote are opponents of
OL,13,Fassisted dying, but keen to see
OL,14,Fdecision-making and regulation lie
OL,15,Fwith politicians in Cardiff, not
OL,16,FLondon.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
